=================================================================================
                        RECOMMENDATIONS
=================================================================================

1. Add pull-up resistors on reset_n in schematic (10k to VCCIO)
2. Add 100nF bypass capacitors on VCORE and VCCIO at package
3. Keep clock routing away from high-speed signals (not applicable here)
4. Consider adding power-down logic if device enters standby mode

No critical recommendations for functional operation.


